---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "December 2024";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - EVSignals" description="EVSignals Terms of Service. Read our terms and conditions for using our services.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          By accessing or using the EVSignals website and services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Description of Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          EVSignals provides electric vehicle market data, analytics, and intelligence services through APIs and other data delivery methods. Our services are designed for business and enterprise use.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. API Usage</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Access to our APIs is subject to separate API Terms and Conditions. By using our APIs, you agree to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Use the APIs only for lawful purposes</li>
          <li>Not exceed rate limits or abuse the service</li>
          <li>Maintain the confidentiality of your API credentials</li>
          <li>Not redistribute data without authorization</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          All content, data, trademarks, and intellectual property on our website and services are owned by EVSignals or our licensors. You may not copy, modify, or distribute our content without prior written consent.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Data Accuracy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          While we strive to provide accurate and timely data, EVSignals does not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of any information provided through our services. Data is provided "as is" and you use it at your own risk.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, EVSignals shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of our services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Indemnification</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          You agree to indemnify and hold harmless EVSignals and its officers, directors, employees, and agents from any claims, damages, or expenses arising from your use of our services or violation of these terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Termination</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          We may terminate or suspend your access to our services at any time, without prior notice, for conduct that we believe violates these Terms of Service or is harmful to other users or our business.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Modifications</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. We will provide notice of significant changes by posting the updated terms on our website.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">10. Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          These Terms of Service shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws, without regard to conflict of law principles.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">11. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:legal@evsignals.com" class="text-green-600 hover:text-green-700">legal@evsignals.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
